Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:55.47,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:59.91,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Look at Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:58.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stupidsta. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:06.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look in this swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:13.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're all sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:17.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That'd probably work great\Nas part of a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:21.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You sort of look like a cow back in Hage...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:25.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you staring at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:23.38,main,Crab,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:25.94,main,Crab,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you told me to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:31.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, I'm so embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.59,main,Crab,0000,0000,0000,,Crab...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:41.06,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Did you all enjoy yet another \Nappearance by me, the great Sekke Bronzazza?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.79,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even more bah-hawesome on the beach!
